# Code Style

- No semicolons, single quotes, tabs, 80 char width (Prettier).
- Import order: React → third-party → `@app` → `@lib` → `@features` → other aliases → relative.
- Tailwind classes sorted by `prettier-plugin-tailwindcss`.
- Run `pnpm format` after large edits; pre-commit runs Prettier via lint-staged.
